ency College, Kolkata">Hindu College</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hindu_Mahila_Vidyalaya" title="Hindu Mahila Vidyalaya">Hindu Mahila Vidyalaya</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Indian_Association_for_the_Cultivation_of_Science" title="Indian Association for the Cultivation of Science">Indian Association for the Cultivation of Science</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Indian_Statistical_Institute" title="Indian Statistical Institute">Indian Statistical Institute</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Jadavpur_University" title="Jadavpur University">National Council of Education, Bengal</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Oriental_Seminary" title="Oriental Seminary">Oriental Seminary</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Presidency_College,_Kolkata" title="Presidency College, Kolkata">Presidency College</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sanskrit_College" title="Sanskrit College">Sanskrit College</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Rammohan_College" title="Rammohan College">Rammohan College</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Surendranath_College" title="Surendranath College">Surendranath College</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Senate_of_Serampore_College_(University)" title="Senate of Serampore College (University)">Serampore College</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/School_of_Tropical_Medicine" title="School of Tropical Medicine">School of Tropical Medicine</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Scottish_Church_College,_Calcutta" title="Scottish Church College, Calcutta">Scottish Church College</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> 